text.tspan: Supplementary Figure 1. Overview of the iModulome. Each node represents an
individual iModulon. Node fill color depicts the species the iModulon was detected in as
per the legend. Node size reflects degree and edge thikcness and colour represent
edge weight as per legend. The network represents the 1500 most highly weighted
edges (< 0.648 edge weight) and was clustered using the MCL clustering method from
the clusterMaker app in Cytoscape v.3.10.2.
